      "name": "target",
      "negativeDescription": undefined,
      "required": undefined,
      "type": "string",
    },
  ],
  "description": "Start the local Fabric MCP HTTP service.

Examples:
  fab serve                              bind 127.0.0.1:7373 (default)
  fab serve --port 8787                  use a custom port
  FABRIC_AUTH_TOKEN=<token> fab serve --host 0.0.0.0   bind non-loopback with Bearer auth",
  "name": "serve",
}
`;

